  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>You can add the <code>fa-paper-plane</code> Font Awesome icon by adding <code>&#x3C;i class=\"fa fa-paper-plane\">&#x3C;/i></code> within your submit <code>button</code> element.</p>\n<p>Give your form's text input field a class of <code>form-control</code>. Give your form's submit button the classes <code>btn btn-primary</code>. Also give this button the Font Awesome icon of <code>fa-paper-plane</code>.</p>\n<p>All textual <code>&#x3C;input></code>, <code>&#x3C;textarea></code>, and <code>&#x3C;select></code> elements with the class <code>.form-control</code> have a width of 100%.</p>\n</section>",
